{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"19790-colores-en-la-calle","title":"Colores en la calle","description":"Hay tanto para ver en las calles. Únete a Sonu, Monu y Rina en una colorida caminata por las calles.","language":"Spanish","langCode":"es","isRtl":false,"level":"1","orientation":"portrait","authors":["Marcelo Alberti"],"illustrators":["Priya Kuriyan"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"StoryWeaver Community","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/19790-colores-en-la-calle"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/703514/size3/2abd90f3ae29e713fad56ce8eb55e637.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/703514/size6/2abd90f3ae29e713fad56ce8eb55e637.jpg"},"audio":null,"pages":[{"n":1,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/26548/size6/3710306f175fc51e9659301727365660.jpg","text":"Sonu se puso una camisa azul luego de su baño. Monu y Rina se pusieron medias azules.","words":null},{"n":2,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/26550/size6/cc5a7192504331c2ba47472f1bb3b180.jpg","text":"¡Oh, estamos todos vestidos con el mismo color hoy! ¡Vengan, vayamos a ver otros colores!","words":null},{"n":3,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/26551/size6/6ebb7e3921f19661d9c0cf0644f1b474.jpg","text":"Aquí están los ajíes rojos de Dadi, ¡No los toquen!","words":null},{"n":4,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/26552/size6/2e1134b683a98c39df3c662ac5152985.jpg","text":"¡Aha! Bholu está cortando berenjenas púrpuras","words":null},{"n":5,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/26553/size6/91e1769c6b2d5484f13ebb52b0b13f8a.jpg","text":"Rani Didi tiene limones amarillos como el sol.","words":null},{"n":6,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/26554/size6/5fc114717f9cb3015ccfde50dd72abee.jpg","text":"Es divertido ver los colores. ¡Y mejor todavía comer algo colorido! ¡Yummy! ¿Comemos este helado rosa?","words":null},{"n":7,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/26555/size6/52f921c4c1eaa03f60f95aaa7d8c6ac6.jpg","text":"¿O mejor un helado blanco?","words":null},{"n":8,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/26556/size6/09fc92689909a4ffff616dfe8b29775e.jpg","text":"Podemos tomar este sabroso jugo verde.","words":null},{"n":9,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/26557/size6/639449f2714f8336e22a7a170cd1f1bb.jpg","text":"O quizás algunos dulces dátiles marrones.","words":null},{"n":10,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/26558/size6/c70f2a1c93ae7a6e7f40153589a92362.jpg","text":"Pero las guavas de Ramu son las mejores.","words":null},{"n":11,"img":"https://storage.googleapis.com/static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/26560/size6/725bc1708ae045ace18704037b1446c3.jpg","text":"¡Son verdes por fuera, rosas por dentro, con pura sal blanca y pimentón rojo!","words":null}],"stats":{"pages":11,"words":111}}